Perfected.definition: completed in accordance with statutory procedure for giving notice and thereby having a status of priority over security interests that are the subject of such procedure at a later date or that are not the subject of such procedure [settling a priority contest between the two security interests]
Perfected.origin: [settling a priority contest between the two security interests]
